name: FloatED-MOON (23) Frez
description:
Hello, my name is Edmoon Holeworld
Humans usually called me The Moon.
Maybe, one day, I became a part of something that made an extinction of a species. Made me be blamed by the society,
and eat my own medicine in the somewhat called prison.
Even if I not change, just call me if you have a problem in your life. I will help you but with an equivalent exchange.
